Package com.peaslimited.shoppeas.service

Interface WholesalerProductService

All Known Implementing Classes:
WholesalerProductServiceImpl
public interface WholesalerProductService
This interface handles operations related to the wholesaler product functionality, such as retrieving, adding, and updating wholesaler products.
